MGME.SettingsAutoInterruptHint: On interrupted scene alteration checks, roll the random event immediately.
MGME.SettingsMinChaosHint: Minimum value for Chaos Factor. Cannot be smaller than 1 or larger than the Maximum Chaos value.
MGME.SettingsMaxChaosHint: Maximum value for Chaos Factor. Maximum is 9 and may not be smaller than Minimum Chaos value.
MGME.Settings3DDelayHint: Rolls Mythic questions slowly, showing the answers as the dice roll. Set to 0 to disable. Larger numbers make it even slower
MGME.Settings3DChaosColorHint: Customize the color of your Chaos Die (Dice so Nice!) for Variations #2 rolls
MGME.SettingsFocusTableHint: Table to use for Random Event focus. Only table names starting with Mythic are listed.

MGME.SettingsActionTableHint: Table to use for Mythic GME Random Event action meaning. Only table names starting with Mythic are listed.
MGME.SettingsSubjectTableHint: Table to use for Mythic GME Random Event subject meaning. Only table names starting with Mythic are listed.
MGME.SettingsAdverbsTableHint: Table to use for Mythic GME V2 Detail Check Descriptor 1 Meaning. Only table names starting with Mythic are listed.
MGME.SettingsAdjectivesTableHint: Table to use for Mythic GME V2 Detail Check Descriptor 2 Meaning. Only table names starting with Mythic are listed.
MGME.SettingsDoubleIgnoreChaosHint: Whether to ignore CF and always hit a random event regardless
